hopobject.body: How long are you planning to stay here? sildegra yorumlar While men spend more time at work, women by far perform more duties around the house. On an average day, women do three times as much housework as men do and more than twice the amount of food preparation and cleaning. Men do lead women in one area of home improvement: lawn and garden care. Men spend an average of 15 minutes per day on this, while women do roughly half that.
